		$$M_o=a_j+\dfrac{m_j-m_{j-1}}{\left(m_j-m_{j-1}\right)+\left(m_j-m_{j+1}\right)} \cdot h=8+\dfrac{11-9}{(11-9)+(11-7)}\cdot 0{,}5=\dfrac{49}{6}\approx8{,}17.$$

