		Do diện tích hình thang bằng $6\sqrt{2}$ nên
		$\dfrac{DC+AB}{2}\cdot{BC}=6\sqrt{2}\Rightarrow DC=1$.\\
		Suy ra $\overrightarrow{DC}=\dfrac{1}{3}\overrightarrow{AB}\Rightarrow\heva{&6-a=\dfrac{1}{3}\\&1-b=\dfrac{-2}{3}\\&-c=\dfrac{-2}{3}}\Leftrightarrow\heva{&a=\dfrac{17}{3}\\&b=\dfrac{5}{3}\\&c=\dfrac{2}{3}}$\\
