		$MN=\sqrt{QN^2+QM^2}=\sqrt{10}$, $PN=\sqrt{NC^2+CP^2}=\dfrac{5}{2}$, $PM=\sqrt{PB^2+BM^2}=\dfrac{\sqrt{13}}{2}$.\\
