 $\dfrac{DB}{DC} = \dfrac{AB}{AC}=\dfrac{1}{3}\Rightarrow \dfrac{\overrightarrow{DB}}{\overrightarrow{DC}}=-\dfrac{1}{3}\Leftrightarrow \overrightarrow{DC}=-3\overrightarrow{DB}$. \,\,\ $(*)$.
