		$AG=\dfrac{2}{3} AM=\dfrac{10\sqrt{3}}{3}$, $SG=\sqrt{SA^2-AG^2}=\dfrac{10\sqrt{6}}{3}$.\\
		Khi đó $S\left(\dfrac{5\sqrt{3}}{3}; 0; \dfrac{10\sqrt{6}}{3}\right)$, $A\left(5\sqrt{3};0;0\right)$, $B(0;-5; 0)$, $C(0; 5; 0)$.\\
