            Ta có $ \mathrm{d}\left(d,\Delta\right)=\mathrm{d}\left(M,d\right)\sqrt{10}\Leftrightarrow\dfrac{\left| c+5\right|}{\sqrt{1^2+(-3)^2}}=\sqrt{10}\Leftrightarrow \hoac{& c=5 \\ &c=-15 }.$\\
