			Mặt khác, ta có $\dfrac{HC}{HL} = \dfrac{QC}{ML} = \dfrac{4}{3} (\text{vì } ML \parallel SC)$.\\
			Mà $2ML = SC$ nên $\dfrac{QC}{SC} = \dfrac{2}{3} \Rightarrow \dfrac{SQ}{SC} = \dfrac{1}{3}$.
