				\itemch \textbf{Sai} Ta có $$\overrightarrow{AC} \cdot \overrightarrow{C'D'} = AC \cdot C'D' \cdot \cos 135^\circ=a\sqrt{2}\cdot a \cdot \left(-\dfrac{\sqrt{2}}{2}\right)=-a^2.$$
