		\]
		Khi đó $R"(x)=0\Leftrightarrow 5\mathrm{e}^{-x}-1=0\Leftrightarrow x=\ln 5$.\\
		Bảng biến thiên
		\begin{center}
			\begin{tikzpicture}[scale=1, line join=round, line cap=round, >=stealth]
			\tkzTabInit[nocadre, lgt=1.5, espcl=2.5, deltacl=0.5]
